REGULATORY DATA NOTICE

The KOSHA regulatory corpus included in this repository
(datasets/kosha/normalized/, datasets/kosha_rag/rag_eval_queries.json)
was collected from KOSHA's public APIs and is subject to KOSHA's
terms of use. This data is provided for research and educational purposes.
Commercial redistribution of the raw corpus data requires separate
clearance from KOSHA (https://www.kosha.or.kr).

The engineering calculation engines implement publicly documented
international standards (ASME, API, IEEE, IEC, AISC, ACI).
The proprietary text of those standards is NOT included in this repository.
